        <p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">Requires two years of personal and business tax returns, Notices of Assessment, business financial statements, and recent bank statements. These offer the lowest rates because the lender can fully verify your income. Best option if your tax returns accurately reflect your income.</p>
        <h3 class="font-montserrat font-semibold text-xl text-[#0d4d3e] mt-8 mb-4">Low Documentation</h3>
