        <div class="bg-[#0d4d3e]/5 border-l-4 border-[#10b981] rounded-r-lg p-6 my-6"><p class="text-[#0d4d3e] font-lato font-light leading-relaxed">In some cases, a low doc application actually results in higher borrowing capacity than full doc — when tax returns show low taxable income due to deductions but bank statements show strong cash flow.</p></div>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-16">
