          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light">Signed income self-declaration</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light">3–6 months business bank statements</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light">Recent BAS statements (if GST-registered)</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light">ID documents</span></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-montserrat font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-[#1e3a5f] mb-6">Tips for Self-Employed Applicants</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 my-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light">Keep personal and business finances separate — dedicated business accounts are much easier for lenders to assess</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light">Lodge tax returns on time — if your most recent return is over 18 months old, many lenders will reject it</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light">Consider whether tax returns understate your income — if so, low doc using bank statements may show a truer picture</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#10b981] mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg><span class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light">Use a broker who understands self-employed lending — not all lenders assess income the same way</span></li>
        </ul>
